headline: Hims & Hers Health and Sociedad Quimica y Minera de Chile have been highlighted as Zacks Bull and Bear of the Day
summary: HWM surges on aerospace demand, rising earnings, and upgraded guidance, while SQM stumbles on weak results and estimate cuts.
